<!-- §9 What is a WiFi smart neon light strip -->
<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What is a WiFi Smart DIY Music Neon Light Strip?</h2>
<p style="color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">A WiFi smart neon light strip is an advanced LED lighting system where each light element can be individually controlled via a smartphone app. Unlike traditional LED strips that light up uniformly, RGBIC strips use integrated circuits in each LED, allowing precise color and brightness control per LED.</p>
<p style="color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">This specific product combines RGBIC technology with music responsiveness and WiFi connectivity. Install the strip along walls, ceilings, or furniture edges. Connect to your home WiFi. Download the app. Now you can create custom color schemes, gradient effects, animated light shows, and even sync everything to your music in real time.</p>
<p style="color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">Available in 5m (300 LEDs) and 10m (960 LEDs) lengths, with shapeable design that bends around corners. Comes with multiple plug standards for different regions. This is professional-grade lighting for creators, gamers, music enthusiasts, and serious vibe architects.</p>

